Katherine Rose Morley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katherine_Rose_Morley 0 Katherine Rose Morley is an actress from Liverpool, England, best known for playing Lucy Garner in The Mill (TV series) in 2013-2014, as Emma Moxam in Thirteen (TV series) and as Ellie Wallace in the British comedy TV Series Last Tango in Halifax starring alongside Derek Jacobi and Sarah Lancashire.
